Largest in Array
Input: arr[] = [1, 8, 7, 56, 90]
Output: 90
Explanation: The largest element of the given array is 90.

CODE:--
class Solution {
    public static int largest(int[] arr) {
        // code here
        int max=arr[0];
        for (int i=0;i<arr.length;i++){
            if (max<arr[i])
            {
                max=arr[i];
            }
        }
        return max;
    }
}
